				["title"] = "For the Light!",
				["text"] = {
					"His name brought Light to darkest Azeroth.\n\nHis valor tore the walls of mis'ry down.\n\nThe Silver Hand would ne'er do better more\n\nthan give the world the knight who'd give himself.",
